title: Prawn Linguine | Jamie’s 15 Minute Meals (2012)
description:
This Prawn Linguine is one of Jamie’s speedy dishes from 15 Minute Meals, and it’s so good! The layers of flavour from cinnamon, saffron, chilli, garlic & lemon give an unexpected, but very welcome twist on a seafood pasta dish, and you really should give it a try!  

Jamie’s 15 Minute Meals originally aired on Channel 4.  If you’re UK based you can watch Jamie programmes on All 4 http://www.channel4.com
